rComments: So sta130 lectures are provided from Dr. White and Prof. Moon. I had to choose Moon cuz a timetable conflict, but through out the semester, I had to self-learn Dr. White's power point even though I never skip Moon's lecture. Her lectures are unorganized, unclear, and too fast. And she refused to upload the annotated version of power point.
Prof. Moon is by far one of the kindest profs I've had at this university so far. She takes the time to make sure you understand all the content and is a great lecturer. 100% would recommend.
